my own community free skiing um and

00:09:04.399 --> 00:09:08.640
everybody who partakes in it. Now um as

00:09:07.600 --> 00:09:11.680
a competitor, I don't want to

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:15.120
generalize, but as a competitor myself,

00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:16.959
I think we yearn the thing we yearn for

00:09:15.120 --> 00:09:18.399
most is a worthy opponent. I think

00:09:16.959 --> 00:09:20.240
there's something so beautiful in that.

00:09:18.399 --> 00:09:21.600
It's not about beating other people, but

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:23.040
it's about this sense of healthy

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:24.640
competition. That's what sportsmanship

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:26.160
is. That's what the Olympics are about.

00:09:24.640 --> 00:09:27.680
If I went to a middle school and like

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:29.279
beat everybody at free skiing there,

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:31.279
it's like not exciting for anybody,

00:09:29.279 --> 00:09:32.880
