00:09:37.519 --> 00:09:40.880
get better and maybe the people at the

00:09:39.440 --> 00:09:42.800
top are contributing a little bit more,

00:09:40.880 --> 00:09:44.959
but everybody is contributing to that

00:09:42.800 --> 00:09:46.320
growth. Um, and and that's something

00:09:44.959 --> 00:09:47.760
that's really special to me. So, do I

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:49.360
welcome that? Yeah, absolutely.

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:50.880
Absolutely. I mean, I love to compete. I

